## âœ… TODO Management

### ğŸ“‹ Get TODO List
- **Endpoint:** `GET /api/todos`
- **Description:** Retrieve all to-do items.
- **Response:**
  ```json
  {
      "message": "Todos retrieved successfully",
      "data": []
  }
  ```

### â• Create TODO
- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/todos`
- **Description:** Create a new to-do item.
- **Request Body:**
```json
{
    "title": "Task title",
    "description": "Task description",
    "completed": false  
}
```
- **Response:**
  ```json
  {
      "message": "Todo added successfully"
  }
  ```

### ğŸ” Get Single TODO
- **Endpoint:** `GET /api/todos/{id}`
- **Description:** Retrieve a single to-do item.
- **Response:**
  - âœ… `200 OK`
  ```json
  {
      "message": "Todo found",
      "data": {}
  }
  ```
  - âŒ `404 Not Found`
  ```json
  {
      "message": "Todo not found"
  }
  ```

### âœï¸ Update TODO
- **Endpoint:** `PUT /api/todos/{id}`
- **Description:** Update an existing to-do item.
- **Request Body:**
```json
{
    "title": "Updated title",
    "description": "Updated description",
    "completed": true
}
```
- **Response:**
  - âœ… `200 OK`
  ```json
  {
      "message": "Todo updated successfully",
      "data": {}
  }
  ```
  - âŒ `404 Not Found`
  ```json
  {
      "message": "Todo not found"
  }
  ```

### ğŸ—‘ï¸ Delete TODO
- **Endpoint:** `DELETE /api/todos/{id}`
- **Description:** Delete a specific to-do item.
- **Response:**
  - âœ… `200 OK`
  ```json
  {
      "message": "Todo deleted successfully"
  }
  ```
  - âŒ `404 Not Found`
  ```json
  {
      "message": "Todo not found"
  }
  ```

### ğŸ—‘ï¸ Delete All TODOs
- **Endpoint:** `DELETE /api/todos`
- **Description:** Delete all to-do items.
- **Response:**
  ```json
  {
      "message": "All todos deleted successfully"
  }
  ```


